Game.....: Charge 'N Blast
Origin...: USA - NTSC
Released.: February 8th, 2001
Ripped.......: Nothing

A radioactive meteor has smashed into the earth wrecking havoc across the globe, causing all manner of insect, reptile, and other assorted creatures to be transformed into gargantuan monsters! You are part of a heavily armed attack force assigned to wipe out the over-sized vermin in this graphically intense shooter. You think you've got what it takes?